          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Same Day Registration Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Help America Vote Act of 2002 to require states with a voter registration requirement to make same-day voter registration available at the polling place on any day voting is permitted.</p>]]></text>
